Sentencas: A full statistical analysis of the microstructure of glass-ceramic solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) seal material, G18, is performed to calculate elastic properties.
Titulo: Statistical continuum mechanics analysis of effective elastic properties in solid oxide fuel cell glass-ceramic seal material

Sentencas: Predictions are made for samples aged for 4h and 1000 h, giving different crystallinity levels.
Titulo: Statistical continuum mechanics analysis of effective elastic properties in solid oxide fuel cell glass-ceramic seal material

Sentencas: Microstructure of the glass-ceramic G18 is characterized by correlation function for each individual phase.
Titulo: Statistical continuum mechanics analysis of effective elastic properties in solid oxide fuel cell glass-ceramic seal material

Sentencas: Predicted results are compared with the Voigt and Reuss bounds in this study.
Titulo: Statistical continuum mechanics analysis of effective elastic properties in solid oxide fuel cell glass-ceramic seal material

Sentencas: The weak contrast analysis results in elastic modulus predictions between the upper and lower bounds but closer to the upper bound.
